.TH GUIX "1" "January 2026" "GNU" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
guix \- manual page for guix 1.5.0rc1.47-fc2f5a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B guix
\fI\,OPTION | COMMAND ARGS\/\fR...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run COMMAND with ARGS, if given.
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
display this helpful text again and exit
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
display version and copyright information and exit
.PP
COMMAND must be one of the sub\-commands listed below:
.IP
main commands
.TP
deploy
deploy operating systems on a set of machines
.TP
describe
describe the channel revisions currently used
.TP
gc
invoke the garbage collector
.TP
